  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td><strong>Handlebars</strong></td>
      <td><code>{{else}}</code> / <code>{{else if}}</code></td>
      <td><code>BlockStatement</code> with <code>program</code> (if-body) + <code>inverse</code> (else-body);
        <code>{{else if}}</code> nests a <code>BlockStatement</code> inside <code>inverse</code>
        (<a href="https://github.com/handlebars-lang/handlebars.js/blob/master/docs/compiler-api.md">compiler-api.md</a>)</td>
      <td>named programs</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><strong>Mustache</strong></td>
      <td><em>(none)</em></td>
      <td>No <code>else</code> — the negative branch is a <strong>separate</strong> inverted section
        <code>{{^name}}…{{/name}}</code>
        (<a href="https://github.com/mustache/spec/blob/master/specs/inverted.yml">inverted.yml</a>)</td>
      <td>separate section</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><strong>Svelte 5</strong></td>
      <td><code>{:else}</code> / <code>{:else if}</code></td>
      <td><code>IfBlock</code>: <code>consequent</code> + <code>alternate</code> (Fragment|null) +
        <code>elseif</code> flag
        (<a href="https://github.com/sveltejs/svelte/blob/main/packages/svelte/src/compiler/types/template.d.ts">template.d.ts</a>)</td>
      <td>named programs</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><strong>Jinja2</strong></td>
      <td><code>{% else %}</code> / <code>{% elif %}</code></td>
      <td><code>class If</code>, <code>fields = ("test","body","elif_","else_")</code>
        (<a href="https://github.com/pallets/jinja/blob/main/src/jinja2/nodes.py">nodes.py</a>)</td>
      <td>named programs</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><strong>Nunjucks</strong></td>
      <td><code>{% else %}</code> / <code>{% elif %}</code></td>
      <td><code>If</code>, <code>fields: ['cond','body','else_']</code>
        (<a href="https://github.com/mozilla/nunjucks/blob/master/nunjucks/src/nodes.js">nodes.js</a>)</td>
      <td>named programs</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><strong>Liquid</strong></td>
      <td><code>{% else %}</code> / <code>{% elsif %}</code></td>
      <td><code>If</code> holds a flat <code>@blocks</code> list of <code>Condition</code> objects;
        <code>else</code> = an <code>ElseCondition</code> sibling
        (<a href="https://github.com/Shopify/liquid/blob/main/lib/liquid/tags/if.rb">if.rb</a>)</td>
      <td>flat sibling list</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><strong>estree</strong> (JS)</td>
      <td><code>else</code></td>
      <td><code>IfStatement { test; consequent; alternate }</code>; <code>else if</code> →
        <code>alternate</code> is an <code>IfStatement</code>
        (<a href="https://github.com/estree/estree/blob/master/es5.md">es5.md</a>)</td>
